{"title":"Hat of Pondering","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Hat_of_Pondering","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.32](/0.32 \"0.32\")**: This article is up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of *Dungeon Crawl Stone Soup*.*\n\n|   |                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n| - | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n|   | The favourite hat of the slug wizard Gastronok, stained with reddish slime and enchanted to aid in his arcane pondering. It has been specially enchanted to protect against the desiccating effects of salt. |\n\n[![Hat of pondering.png](/images/d/df/Hat_of_pondering.png)](/File:Hat_of_pondering.png) ***the +3 hat of Pondering***\n\n+3 [hat](/Hat \"Hat\")\n\n[Ponderousness](/Ponderousness \"Ponderousness\") ego  \n+40 [Willpower](/Willpower \"Willpower\") (Will+)  \n+5 [Intelligence](/Intelligence \"Intelligence\")  \n+10 [MP](/MP \"MP\")\n\n## Desirability\n\nThe **hat of Pondering**[\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1) provides great bonuses to spellcasting, and a useful will bonus on top. However, the movement penalty can be dangerous - it makes retreat more difficult. Luckily, this hat is most beneficial to those who are likely to have the means to speed themselves up, i.e. mages with spells like [Swiftness](/Swiftness \"Swiftness\") or [Blink](/Blink \"Blink\").\n\nCharacters which are faster or slower than usual have unique interactions with the Hat of Pondering:\n\n- [Cheibriados](/Cheibriados \"Cheibriados\") worshippers, [Barachim](/Barachim \"Barachim\"), and [Nagas](/Naga \"Naga\") are already slower than usual; they don't mind being slower (as much as others).\n- [Armataurs](/Armataur \"Armataur\") wearing the [lightning scales](/Lightning_scales \"Lightning scales\") move fast; having ponderousness puts them back at normal speed.\n- [Spriggans](/Spriggan \"Spriggan\") can still outrun normal-speed monsters, but are unable to outrun [hasted](/Haste \"Haste\") normal-speed monsters. Wearing this hat drops Spriggans from 166% to 142% move speed, making them slower than certain enemies (such as [centaurs](/Centaur \"Centaur\"), [juggernauts](/Juggernaut \"Juggernaut\"), [Mennas](/Mennas \"Mennas\"), and [orbs of fire](/Orbs_of_fire \"Orbs of fire\")).\n\nTrue to its lore, the hat of Pondering is sometimes found on [Gastronok](/Gastronok \"Gastronok\") (10% chance).\n\n## References\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [art-data.txt:1154](https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.32.0/crawl-ref/source/art-data.txt#L1154) (0.32.0)\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Hat of Pondering - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Hat_of_Pondering\",\"wgTitle\":\"Hat of Pondering\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":81232,\"wgRevisionId\":81232,\"wgArticleId\":4432,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"0.32 articles\",\"Unrands\",\"Headgear\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\"